export default function WineCard({ wine }) { return (
Winery: {wine.winery}
Year: {wine.year}
Grape: {wine.grape}
Fruit: {wine.fruit} / 5
Acidity: {wine.acidity} /5
Tannins: {wine.tannins} / 5
Body: {wine.body} / 5
Dominant Flavors: {wine.dominantFlavors.map(flavor =>
{flavor}
)}
PossibleFlavors Flavors: {wine.arrPossibleFlavors.map(flavor =>
{flavor}
)}
Overall Rating: {wine.overallRating}
) }
